Extract Data from the 4 Datasets in Excel Sources to Staging Area in OLE DB Destinations 8

Double click on the PackageStaging.dtsx. If it’s the first time, you will be presented with a blank pane on the Control Flow Task. 

·         Drag and drop a Sequence Container from the SSIS Toolbox on to the pane. Rename the container with an appropriate name – SeqCont-Loading the Staging Tables

·         Drag and drop 4 Data Flow Tasks from SSIS Toolbox on to the Sequence Container above for the 4 datasets and name them appropriately as shown in the screenshot below:

 


 

·         Double click on the first Data Flow Task to configure the extraction of the first dataset as below screenshot:

 













 

·         Repeat the above for the other 3 Datasets.
